verses.text_plain: The fool hath said in his heart, There is no God. They are corrupt, they have done abominable works, there is none that doeth good.
verses.verse_html: 1The fool hath said in his heart, There is no God. They are corrupt, they have done abominable works, there is none that doeth good.

verses.text_plain: The Lord looked down from heaven upon the children of men, to see if there were any that did understand, and seek God.
verses.verse_html: 2The Lord looked down from heaven upon the children of men, to see if there were any that did understand, and seek God.

verses.text_plain: They are all gone aside, they are all together become filthy: there is none that doeth good, no, not one.
verses.verse_html:
3They are all gone aside, they are all together become filthy: there is none that doeth good, no, not one. ▼
▼ filthy: Heb. stinking

verses.text_plain: Have all the workers of iniquity no knowledge? who eat up my people as they eat bread, and call not upon the Lord.
verses.verse_html: 4Have all the workers of iniquity no knowledge? who eat up my people as they eat bread, and call not upon the Lord.

verses.text_plain: There were they in great fear: for God is in the generation of the righteous.
verses.verse_html:
5There were they in great fear: for God is in the generation of the righteous. ▼
▼ were…: Heb. they feared a fear

footnotes.body_text: ▼ were…: Heb. they feared a fear
footnotes.body_html: ▼ were…: Heb. they feared a fear

verses.text_plain: Ye have shamed the counsel of the poor, because the Lord is his refuge.
verses.verse_html: 6Ye have shamed the counsel of the poor, because the Lord is his refuge.

verses.text_plain: Oh that the salvation of Israel were come out of Zion! when the Lord bringeth back the captivity of his people, Jacob shall rejoice, and Israel shall be glad.
verses.verse_html:
7Oh that the salvation of Israel were come out of Zion! when the Lord bringeth back the captivity of his people, Jacob shall rejoice, and Israel shall be glad. ▼
▼ Oh…: Heb. Who will give

footnotes.body_html: ▼ Oh…: Heb. Who will give
